<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>CUDA by Example</title>
    <link rel=stylesheet href="site.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="intro">
      <h2><a href="./">CUDA by Example</a></h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-toolkit">CUDA</a> is NVIDIA's
        parallel computing platform and programming model for GPU-accelerated computing.
      </p>

      <p>
        <em>CUDA by Example</em> is a hands-on introduction to CUDA using annotated
        example programs. Check out the <a href="hello-world">first example</a> or
        browse the full list below.
      </p>

      <p>
        Examples target CUDA 12.x and assume a basic familiarity with C/C++.
      </p>

      <ul>
      {{range .}}
        <li><a href="{{.ID}}">{{.Name}}</a></li>
      {{end}}
      </ul>
{{ template "footer" }}
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
